Basically, if my known good configs are used, just install the below
applications from ports, load my config files, and restart everything. 

 /usr/ports/mail/postfix
make install clean

/usr/ports/dovecot
make install clean

/usr/ports/security/amavisd-new
make install clean

/usr/ports/security/clamav
make install clean

/usr/ports/databases/p5-BerkeleyDB
make install clean

/usr/ports/mail/p5-Mail-SpamAssassin
make install clean
